- Make the audit trail easy to scan.
- Include filters by date and usage type.

2.38 Build pricing controls for admin view
- Show editable price per SFT.
- Show discount tiers.
- Make it obvious this is an operator/admin control area.

2.39 Build revenue summary
- Daily revenue
- Monthly revenue
- Trend comparison
- Show relative growth or decline.

2.40 Build transaction history table
- Include transaction type, amount, reference, date, and status.
- Support export-like UI actions, even if mocked.

PHASE 8 — PAYMENTS MODULE

2.41 Build invoice management table
- Include:
