PHASE 10 — OCR / AI UPLOADS MODULE

2.49 Build file upload area
- Support image and PDF drag-and-drop UI.
- Show upload instructions and supported file hints.
- Simulate file drop, upload progress, and completion.

2.50 Build file preview panel
- Display uploaded document preview.
- Show file metadata.
- Allow switching between uploaded files.

2.51 Build OCR extraction preview
- Show extracted measurements.
- Show material detection results.
- Highlight confidence and possible inaccuracies.

2.52 Build AI suggestion panel
- Display:
  - suggested dimensions
  - detected components
  - inferred values
- Keep it obviously simulated, but convincing.

2.53 Build validation interface
- Highlight errors.
- Allow manual corrections.
- Mark validated vs unresolved fields.
- Add accept/reject flow for extracted values.

PHASE 11 — REPORTS (CA / GST) MODULE

2.54 Build GST summary cards
