- Offline events

PHASE 14 — OFFLINE MODE SIMULATION

2.66 Build offline indicator
- Show clear offline badge.
- Add a working-offline banner.
- Make the state impossible to miss.

2.67 Build sync queue panel
- Show pending actions.
- Show sync order.
- Show status per queued item.

2.68 Build manual sync button
- Trigger mock synchronization.
- Show completed / failed sync states.
- Keep the experience realistic.

PHASE 15 — MULTI-LANGUAGE SUPPORT

2.69 Build language switcher
- English
- Telugu
- Hindi

2.70 Simulate translated UI text
- Switch visible labels and navigation text.
- Keep iconography constant.
- Demonstrate the app can support multiple business-user languages.

2.71 Ensure layout stability across languages
- Verify longer/shorter labels do not break the UI.
- Maintain spacing and component integrity.

PHASE 16 — POLISH, QUALITY, AND REALISM

2.72 Improve all loading states
- Skeletons
- Spinners
- Placeholder cards
- Table loading states

2.73 Improve all empty states
- No projects
- No inventory
- No invoices
